data.description: REDUCED TO SELL! An Amazing opportunity to purchase a beautiful home in Saga Bay. Huge private & gated lot with room for your boat, RV, a swimming pool with waterfall. Pool pump 2020. Pool deck has pavers. Beautiful curb appeal, vaulted ceilings, Roof 2019, impact windows and doors 2023, formal living room and large dining room, family room, perfect for large gatherings, very functional and well designed kitchen overlooks family room, spacious indoor laundry room, huge bedrooms with ample closet space, master bath offers tub and separate shower, both bathrooms were updated in 2022, split floor plan, AC 2022 with warranty for parts. 2-car garage. Rarely available.  Don't miss out on making this your Dream Home.  Sellers are motivated.   Easy to Show.
